text: Trichosophroniella rotschildi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae, and the only species in the genus Trichosophroniella. It was described by Breuning in 1959.Biolib.cz - Trichosophroniella rotschildi. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphorini Category:Beetles described in 1959
